column5: Just a video of some carp fishing during the pre spawn on a Lake Erie trib. I pretty much got skunked this day but Eric got his PB.    Sorry, dunno how to embed into post..
Uuuuuuuugggggly.      But large....looks like a blast
Nice video!  They certainly are fun to catch and they are more than willing on most days.  WR
It wouldn't be carp fishing in SW Ontario without an old tire nearby...not my bag but looks like good fun
Some nice fights and great video ! That 30 lbr is a cow Thanks for sharing.
